These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-1::.
There 2 different types of food: nectarine, pear
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: may, september
1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far left##1
2. the person who's birthday is in september is not the person eating pear##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | pear   | nectarine  |
| Sport   | may | september |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-2::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, tiparillo
2 different pets are kept: goat, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
2. the owner of the goat is not the tiparillo-smoker##6

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1   |     2      |
| Food   | blend | tiparillo      |
| Pet    | goat  | guinea-pig |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-3::.
City: london, venice
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: handball, sailing
1. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
2. the person who's sport is handball is not the person traveling to london##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |
| Food    | venice  | london    |
| Sport   | handball | sailing |

